Introduction

AEONIT is a 5-member South Korean boy virtual idol group under ONMIND. They debuted on August 28, 2024, with their first single album, LUMOS.

Their name is a combination of the word “aeonian” which means for eternity and “emit” which means sending out light, sound, etc. It means that they will be sending out their own light and sound for their fans who give their love and support in order for them to exist.
